# Email template notifications

Inventory of **when** FreeCRM sends from `u_yf_emailtemplates`, **how** the template is chosen, and **where** that is configured. Transport/queue details → `mail-module.mdc`. Manual compose UI → `mail-compose.mdc`. Matrix UI → `recruitment-settings.mdc`. Apply/relation side effects → `recruitment-project-candidates.mdc`.

## Shared plumbing

| Piece | Role |
|-------|------|
| `u_yf_emailtemplates` | Store: `sys_name`, `modules`, `is_system`, `account_id`, subject/body |
| `App\Email\Mail::getTemplete($id\|sys_name)` | Load template |
| `Outbound::sendFromTemplate*` | Immediate enqueue → `s_yf_mail_queue` → `MailerTask` |
| `Email\Delayed\Buffer` | Delay → `s_yf_delayed_email_queue` → cron `DelayedEmailQueueTask` → mail queue |
| Gates | `isActiveSendingMails`, default SMTP, recipient has email |

Template identity for automation: prefer **`sys_name`** (stable). Numeric ids only in legacy workflow tasks / manual preselect. `is_system=1` hides from compose picker; matrix/cron/workflows still resolve by `sys_name`.

Footer field on EmailTemplates: `$(dynamic : …)$` → TemplateElements (`PLL_VARIABLE_ALIAS`). Appended at send/preview via `Mail::appendParsedFooter` → `<div class="fc-email-content">…</div><div class="fc-email-footer" contenteditable="false">…</div>`. **Put signature/unsubscribe tokens in the `footer` column**, not in `content` — content-baked footers skip wrappers (compose AI must fall back to signature heuristics). Bulk fix: `m260723_000004` (extract from `content` → `footer`). `TextParser::dynamic()` also wraps known mail footer codes (`current_user_footer`, `standard_user_footer`, `*_recruitment_group_footer`, `candidates_unsubscribe_footer`, `tracking_logo`) in `.fc-email-footer` when expanded inside body.

| Alias | Body | Use |
|-------|------|-----|
| `current_user_footer` | `standard_user_footer` | personal / consultant mails (`$(generator : …)` = CurrentUser) |
| `current_recruitment_group_footer` | `recruitment_group_footer` | system/group mails (rekrutacja@; no user generators) |

Plus `candidates_unsubscribe_footer` when mailing Candidates. Do not use old codes `current_footer` / `standard_footer` (renamed `m260720_000004`).

**Footer layout:** `recruitment_group_footer` — greeting + logo **stacked** (logo under text, ~80px). Do not put wide `$(organization : mailLogo)$` in a side column next to text — email clients ignore cell width and text overlaps the logo (`m260720_000006`).

**Auto-mail TextParser contract (Candidates + project):** `record` = candidate, `sourceRecord` = project. Project fields (e.g. `nazwa_projektu`) must use `$(sourceRecord : …)$`, not `$(record : …)$`.

**Re-test apply mail:** `createLink` only on new membership — use an **Aktywna** project the candidate is not already linked to, else no mail.

## Recruitment — send paths

| Trigger | Entry | Template select | Config | Delivery |
|---------|-------|-----------------|--------|----------|
| Kanban / DashBoard status drag | `ChangeCandidateStatusManuallyAjax` → `RecruitmentStatusTransitionMail` | matrix `short_name` → `RecruitmentTemplate::resolveShortNamesForAccount(project.kontrahent)` | Settings › Rekrutacja › TransitionMail → `u_yf_recruitment_status_transition_mail` | per row `prompt` (modal) or `auto` (server Outbound) |
| Screening Reject (`PPL_APPLIED` → `PPL_REJECTED_AFTER_CV`) | `RejectCandidateManuallyAjax` → `ScreeningRejectionMail::enqueueDelayedRejectionMail` | `REASON_SYS_NAMES` → Candidates `sys_name` | **code** map + seeded templates (`m260714_000003_…`) | delayed buffer (`STATUS_CHANGE`); cancel on revert out of reject |
| Screening Accept | `AcceptCandidateManuallyAjax` | — | — | **no mail** from Accept |
| Relation workflow (`ON_RELATION_MODIFY`) | `GetRelatedMembers::changeStatus` → `RelationWorkflowRunner` → `VTEmailTemplateTask` | task field `template` (numeric id) | Settings Workflows + `com_vtiger_workflow_relation_triggers`; hub `…&module=Recruitment&view=Workflows` | delayed buffer when buffer enabled |
| Manual compose / mass email / matrix `prompt` | `IndividualSendMailModal` → `Base\Actions\Mail` | user pick (hides `is_system`); optional `templateIds` | EmailTemplates records | immediate after user confirm |
| CV apply / `PPL_APPLIED` create | `GetRelatedMembers::createLink` → `ApplicationReceivedMail::sendForAppliedLink` | `sys_name` `kandydaci_potwierdzenie_otrzymania_aplikacji` via `RecruitmentTemplate::resolveShortNamesForAccount` | template must be `sender_type=system_smtp` + recruitment `smtp_id` (rekrutacja@; migration `m260720_000001`); footer = `current_recruitment_group_footer` + `candidates_unsubscribe_footer` (`m260720_000002`/`000003`); project fields via **`$(sourceRecord : …)$`** (record = Candidates) | immediate Outbound; From = system SMTP, not user mailbox |

CV import ops errors use raw `ImportErrorMailer` (not EmailTemplates). Manual / AI link (`PPL_MANUALLY_ADDED` / `PPL_AI_ADDED`) does **not** send confirmation.

**Screening reject** (`ScreeningRejectionMail`): `modules=Candidates` (recipient = candidate; project = `sourceRecord` — do **not** move to ProjektyRekrutacyjne). **`is_system=1`** (`m260723_000002`). Placeholders: `$(sourceRecord : nazwa_projektu)$` (`m260723_000003`). Seed footer = `current_user_footer` + `candidates_unsubscribe_footer` in **`footer`** column (`m260714_000003`). Map: `NO_EXPERIENCE` → `kandydaci_odrzucenie_brak_doswiadczenia`; `MISSING_SKILLS` → `…_brak_kompetencji`; `PROFILE_FIT` → `…_niedopasowanie_profilu`; `MISSING_POLISH_LANGUAGE` → `…_brak_jezyka_polskiego`; `OTHER_CANDIDATE_CHOSEN` → `…_inny_kandydat`; `PROJECT_CLOSED` → `…_proces_zamkniety`.

**Dev TransitionMail matrix (example):** screening-pass → interview invite `kandydaci_zaproszenie_na_rozmowe` (`prompt`); interview → to-client consent `kandydaci_zgoda_na_przetwarzanie_danych` (`prompt`). Matrix is **per-DB** (not in `pushsrc`).

### Relation-workflow pitfall

`com_vtiger_workflow_relation_triggers.destination_module` may still be **`Kandydaci`** while runtime uses **`Candidates`** → matcher fails → WF never sends (e.g. WF 79 invite). Fix trigger rows to `Candidates` if relation email WFs should run. Prefer TransitionMail matrix for new recruitment mails.

## Other modules (pattern only)

| Path | Select | Notes |
|------|--------|-------|
| Record workflow `VTEmailTemplateTask` | task `template` id (HelpDesk often `sys_name` string) | immediate Outbound |
| `VTEmailTask` | freeform subject/body | not EmailTemplates table |
| Calendar `SendReminderTask` | sys_name `ActivityReminderNotification*` | cron |
| `NotificationsTask` | `SendNotificationsViaMail` | digest cron |
| Forgot password / BruteForce | fixed sys_name | security events |
| Scheduled reports | template id in report | schedule |

## Settings / DB cheat sheet

| What | Where |
|------|-------|
| Transition mail matrix | `index.php?module=Recruitment&parent=Settings&view=TransitionMail` |
| Relation WF hub | `index.php?module=Recruitment&parent=Settings&view=Workflows` |
| EmailTemplates CRUD | `index.php?module=EmailTemplates&view=ListView` |
| Delayed buffer UI | `index.php?module=DelayedEmails&view=ListView` |
| Outbound queue | Settings › E-maile do wysłania (`mail-module.mdc`) |

**Tables:** `u_yf_emailtemplates`, `u_yf_recruitment_status_transition_mail`, `com_vtiger_workflows` / `com_vtiger_workflowtasks`, `com_vtiger_workflow_relation_triggers`, `s_yf_delayed_email_queue`, `s_yf_mail_queue`.
